PATHS - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-clns-isis-oper:isis/instances/instance/{instance-name}/topologies/topology/ipv4-routes/ipv4-route/native-status/native-details/backup/paths/

Retrieve operation of resource: paths

instance-name: string
in path

ID of instance-name

200 OK
paths_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

"interface-name-xr": "string", Interface name

      
"checkpoint-object-id": "integer", Checkpoint object ID

      
"checkpoint-interface-handle": "string", Local interface handle

      
"dis-areas": "string" Areas in which this system is DIS

    }
  ]
}
